arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	idKseniaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_KseniaDoor)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idKseniaClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idKseniaClone, loc_KseniaWalkTo, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idKseniaClone, loc_KseniaWalkTo)
	
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idKseniaClone, "NPC_Idle_Stand_Ritual_Strong")
		Hydra.QActorWait(idKseniaClone, 0.5)
	
		Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idKseniaClone, loc_SpellAimAt, fx_SpellRope, true)
		Hydra.QActorWait(idKseniaClone, 1.0)
	
		Hydra.QActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idKseniaClone, fx_SpellRope)
		Hydra.QActorWait(idKseniaClone, 0.5)

		Hydra.QActorEventSendToActor(idKseniaClone, "OpenCarthasDoor", idSelf)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idKseniaClone, "NPC_F_Base_event_strong_idle")
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_Ksenia01b, idActorPlayer, idKseniaClone)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idKseniaClone, conv_Ksenia01b)
		
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idKseniaClone, loc_KseniaDungeonWalkTo, "NPC_Walk_Fast", false)

		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idKseniaClone, 1.5)
	end
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	idKseniaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_KseniaStand)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idKseniaClone) then
	
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idKseniaClone, loc_LeaveChapel, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
		--Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationConstantSpeed(idKseniaClone, loc_LeaveChapel, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_RUN, false)
		
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idKseniaClone, 1.5)
	end

end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(gizmo_DungeonDoor) then
		idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	
		Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(gizmo_DungeonDoor, idQuestOwner, false)
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, sWorldName)
	if Hydra.ActorGetLevelArea(idActorPlayer) == "Hawe_Zakarum_Keep2" then
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("OpenCarthasDoor", idSelf, idSelf)

--		Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(gizmo_DungeonDoor, idActorPlayer, false)
	end
end
